# OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor noise
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.bak

# Local notes / scratch (anything starting with _ is treated as personal scratch)
_*

# Anything the user accidentally drops in that contains real client data
**/draft-*.docx
**/draft-*.pdf

# Contractor-specific filled-in profiles must never reach the public repo.
# The pattern catches IQ-your-contractor-profile.md, IQ-anything.md, and
# any [contractor]-your-contractor-profile.md style file.
IQ-*
*-iq.md
*-filled.md
**/your-contractor-profile-*.md
